      "message": "I thought we agreed that service layer will return the response for all requests and controller will filter it out.\n\nDmiPluginRegistrationErrorResponse is a generated class and is a POJO so not sure if we should keep it here.\n\nThe Controller should call a method to find failed responses but I was not sure if I want to create a separate class for this logic. \n\nI agree that it is not a perfect place for this logic but I could not find a good split to create a separate class, so decided to keep it here for now.\n\nAny suggestions are welcome.",
